&lt;p&gt;As the leading transit bus manufacturer in the United States, GILLIG buses play a critical role in the environmental and social initiatives in communities across our nation.&amp;nbsp; GILLIG is on the forefront in the transition to zero-emission vehicles and has an unmatched reputation in the industry for quality, reliability, durability, service, and support.&amp;nbsp; From initial design through final assembly, each GILLIG bus is designed and built in Livermore, CA.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY GILLIG&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leader in environmentally friendly mobility solutions including battery electric, hybrid electric, near-zero CNG and clean diesel transit buses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Renowned for its inclusive team/family-oriented culture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stable, successful, and growing organization – a Bay Area business for over 132 years!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible schedules (*depending on project needs)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent compensation including company paid medical premiums, generous retirement plan and other comprehensive benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you looking for a stable company in an industry that supports critical US Infrastructure?&amp;nbsp; Do you want to make a difference every day and join an amazing team of Procurement Professionals that take pride in what we do?&amp;nbsp; Then GILLIG might be the place for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a driven and detail-oriented Supply Chain Professional with a background in manufacturing or related field.&amp;nbsp; Our Buyers are responsible for planning, negotiating, and purchasing components in support of our manufacturing facility in Livermore, California.&amp;nbsp; The ideal candidate would consistently:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a team player that excels in maximizing Supplier Performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertly manage competing priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and lead initiatives to reduce cost and increase service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access risk and proactively resolve potential issues with continuity of supply&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with multiple departments, including Engineering, Quality Assurance,&amp;nbsp;Production, Sales and Warehouse to optimize GILLIG’s Supply Chain and ensure production material is stocked as required&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan and place purchase orders, with appropriate Lead Time for assigned commodities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expedite and resolve issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, evaluate, and integrate new suppliers and technologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve operational efficiency in the supply chain&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage supplier relationships and be the point of contact for all supplier issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Investigate, determine root cause, and resolve for inventory and invoicing discrepancies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the continuous improvement of quality, service and total cost in support of our business goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performs other duties as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Through individual contributions, established procedures and cross functional influencing, GILLIG’s Buyers ensure all materials, services, and supplies are available as required to support GILLIG Production. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
