&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BA/BS or equivalent work experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years previous experience in a purchasing or supply chain role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Supplier Managed Inventory Contracts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving skills, organization skills,

