&lt;li&gt;Ensure timely and accurate payroll execution in compliance with federal, state, and local regulations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and maintain payroll policies, procedures, and internal controls.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee payroll tax compliance, garnishments, deductions, earnings, and benefit-related payroll transactions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead payroll audits, reconciliations, tax filings, and year-end activities including W-2 processing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead, mentor, and develop payroll staff while serving as the escalation point for complex payroll issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary payroll system administrator and subject matter expert for SAP SuccessFactors Employee Central Payroll&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee payroll integrations and data accuracy between UKG Time &amp;amp; Attendance (Kronos), HRIS, payroll, and financial systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop payroll metrics, dashboards, reporting, and process improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
